text: Chen Qiaolin (, born September 2, 1996) is a Chinese road and track cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . Competing in the team pursuit she won a gold medal at the 2017 Asian Championships and a silver at the 2018 Asian Games. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Chinese female cyclists Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Cyclists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for China Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games medalists in cycling
